* {{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=12&hitYear=2014&termGbn=month|title=Online Download – December 2014|publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association|work=Gaon Chart|accessdate=May 15, 2015|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150623055131/http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=12&hitYear=2014&termGbn=month|archivedate=June 23, 2015}}
* {{cite web|url=http://gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/chart/online.gaon?nationGbn=T&serviceGbn=S1020&targetTime=2015&hitYear=2015&termGbn=year|title=Online Download – 2015|publisher=Korea Music Content Industry Association|work=Gaon Chart|accessdate=January 11, 2016}}
