| quote = "I have this disease-like need to try to create something new. When you’re kind of being chased, and everything you do goes so well, you develop this sickness and a sense of need to constantly do something different."<br>— G-Dragon<ref name="complex">{{cite web| title =G-Dragon's 15 Favorite Albums | work= Complex Magazine| date =September 13, 2013 |url =http://www.complex.com/music/2013/09/g-dragon-favorite-albums-of-all-time/ | accessdate = October 14, 2016}}</ref>
